```

---

## 5. Functional Requirements

### 5.1 Trial Registration
- Sponsors must register each clinical trial.
- Each trial must reference a registered product.
- Mandatory protocols must be uploaded.
- System validates trial completeness.

### 5.2 Document Management
- Supports PDF, DOCX, XLSX.
- Max file size: 100 MB.
- Maintains full audit history.

### 5.3 Review Process
- Trials are assigned to qualified reviewers.
- Reviewers may request protocol amendments.
- Multiple review cycles are supported.
- All decisions are logged.

### 5.4 Decision Management
- Decisions: Approved, Rejected, Suspended
- Ethics justification is mandatory.
- Digital approval is required.

### 5.5 Safety Monitoring
- Adverse events must be reported within 24 hours.
- Risk scores are calculated automatically.
- High-risk trials generate alerts.

---

## 6. Business Rules

| Rule ID | Description                                              |
|---------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| BR-01   | Trials cannot proceed without ethics approval            |
| BR-02   | Only certified reviewers may approve protocols           |
| BR-03   | Suspended trials require executive review                |
| BR-04   | Serious adverse events reviewed within 24 hours          |
| BR-05   | Trials with repeated violations are flagged              |

---

