## 8. Database Schema

### 8.1 sponsors

| Column        | Type         | Description               |
|---------------|--------------|---------------------------|
| sponsor_id    | INT (PK)     | Unique identifier         |
| company_name  | VARCHAR(200) | Registered organization   |
| contact_email | VARCHAR(150) | Primary email             |
| license_no    | VARCHAR(50)  | Regulatory license number |

---

### 8.2 products

| Column          | Type         | Description                         |
|-----------------|--------------|-------------------------------------|
| product_id      | INT (PK)     | Product identifier                  |
| product_name    | VARCHAR(200) | Name of product                     |
| category        | VARCHAR(100) | Drug/Device/Biologic                |
| risk_class      | VARCHAR(50)  | Risk category                       |
| sponsor_id      | INT (FK)     | References sponsors.sponsor_id      |

---

### 8.3 trials

| Column        | Type         | Description                       |
|---------------|--------------|-----------------------------------|
| trial_id      | INT (PK)     | Trial ID                          |
| sponsor_id    | INT (FK)     | Sponsor                           |
| product_id    | INT (FK)     | Product                           |
| status        | VARCHAR(50)  | Draft/Submitted/Approved/Suspended|
| start_date    | DATE         | Trial start date                  |
| last_updated  | TIMESTAMP    | Last update time                  |

---

### 8.4 documents

| Column       | Type         | Description              |
|--------------|--------------|--------------------------|
| document_id  | INT (PK)     | Document ID              |
| trial_id     | INT (FK)     | Related trial            |
| document_type| VARCHAR(100) | Protocol/Consent/Report  |
| version      | INT          | Version number           |
| file_path    | VARCHAR(500) | Storage path             |
| upload_date  | DATE         | Upload date              |

---

### 8.5 reviewers

| Column              | Type         | Description        |
|---------------------|--------------|--------------------|
| reviewer_id         | INT (PK)     | Reviewer ID        |
| name                | VARCHAR(150) | Reviewer name      |
| certification_level | VARCHAR(50)  | Certification tier |
| department          | VARCHAR(100) | Department         |

---

### 8.6 reviews

| Column       | Type        | Description      |
|--------------|-------------|------------------|
| review_id    | INT (PK)    | Review ID        |
| trial_id     | INT (FK)    | Trial            |
| reviewer_id  | INT (FK)    | Reviewer         |
| review_status| VARCHAR(50) | Pending/Approved |
| comments     | TEXT        | Review notes     |
| review_date  | DATE        | Review date      |

---

### 8.7 safety_reports

| Column        | Type        | Description          |
|---------------|-------------|----------------------|
| report_id     | INT (PK)    | Report ID            |
| trial_id      | INT (FK)    | Trial                |
| severity      | VARCHAR(50) | Minor/Major/Critical |
| description   | TEXT        | Event details        |
| reported_date | DATE        | Date reported        |
| risk_score    | INT         | Calculated score     |

---

### 8.8 compliance_actions

| Column          | Type        | Description          |
|-----------------|-------------|----------------------|
| action_id       | INT (PK)    | Action ID            |
| report_id       | INT (FK)    | Safety report        |
| action_type     | VARCHAR(100)| Inspection/Warning   |
| status          | VARCHAR(50) | Open/Closed          |
| resolution_date | DATE        | Completion date      |

