## 11. Example Queries

### Q1: Active Trials

```sql
SELECT *
FROM trials
WHERE status = 'Approved';
```

### Q2: High-Risk Safety Reports

```sql
SELECT t.trial_id, COUNT(s.report_id) AS critical_events
FROM trials t
JOIN safety_reports s
ON t.trial_id = s.trial_id
WHERE s.severity = 'Critical'
GROUP BY t.trial_id;
```

### Q3: Reviewer Activity

```sql
SELECT r.name, COUNT(rv.review_id) AS total_reviews
FROM reviewers r
JOIN reviews rv
ON r.reviewer_id = rv.reviewer_id
GROUP BY r.name;
```

---

## 12. Error Handling

| Scenario              | System Behavior     |
|-----------------------|---------------------|
| Missing protocol      | Block submission    |
| Invalid consent form  | Reject upload       |
| Safety report delay   | Auto-escalation     |
| System failure        | Rollback            |
